      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Smart mare COOL AND CLASSY (5) backs up off a winning return four days ago, getting home by 7 metres at Redcliffe. Has recorded four wins and a placing from five second-up attempts so should only be improved and showed her class by winning last season's NSW Oaks. Has a phenomenal record at this circuit and distance, winning 10 of 12. The one to beat. SWEET DIOR NZ (2) has been racing very well and added to a string of wins and placings when scoring by 2.2 metres at this circuit and distance last time. Should enjoy a nice run from this lower starting position so could challenge. SEASIDE GLORY (6) is flying at present with two successive wins at this circuit and distance. Draws wider but could keep the ball rolling. GOLDEN SHOOZ (7) draws wider but is open to improvement off a third when resuming here two weeks ago.",
